001package io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.table.insertion;
002
003import io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.base.ComponentType;
004import lombok.AllArgsConstructor;
005import lombok.Getter;
006
007/**
008 * Represents a configuration for inserting values into a table cell.
009 *
010 * <p>This component defines the insertion mechanism using a specified
011 * {@link ComponentType}, along with its order of execution.
012 *
013 * <p>It is primarily used in {@code CellLocator} and {@code TableImpl}.
014 *
015 * @author Cyborg Code Syndicate üíçüë®üíª
016 */
017@AllArgsConstructor
018@Getter
019public class CellInsertionComponent {
020
021   /**
022    * The type of component used for insertion.
023    */
024   private Class<? extends ComponentType> type;
025
026   /**
027    * The specific component type identifier.
028    */
029   private String componentType;
030
031   /**
032    * The execution order for insertion, determining priority when multiple insertions occur.
033    */
034   int order;
035}
